Yeah, this is actually one of my favorite boots in the entire line. I can

00:00:24.560 --> 00:00:28.680
pick whatever boot I want and this, often times, is the one I gravitate toward

00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:32.790
just 'cause it's a great mix of comfort and performance

00:00:32.810 --> 00:00:36.830
and awesome for a guy that's riding a lot of freestyle terrain

00:00:36.850 --> 00:00:40.980
so couple things that help set this apart from

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.100
any other boot out there is going to be the fact that it's got

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:49.190
what we call a Cross Bone Tech which, it's got an articulating cuff on the inside.

00:00:49.210 --> 00:00:53.260
And, actually, a little carbon rod stitched on the outside.

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:57.390
So, you can flex inward where you want that flex to grab your board and

