00:01:17.820 --> 00:01:21.860
which is on lower end boots, it's going 

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:25.990
to actually have a cuff that links this liner down into the shell so it makes them become more

00:01:26.010 --> 00:01:30.080
of a single unit really, gives you more of a heel hold in this boot.

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:34.160
